sections.heading: Water Officer; survey of streams
sections.text: The Chief Water Officer may make surveys of streams showing location of possible water power developments and irrigation projects.SourceLaws 1919, c. 190, tit. VII, art. V, div. 2, ยง 30, p. 845;C.S.1922, ยง 8449;C.S.1929, ยง 81-6330;R.S.1943, ยง 46-212;Laws 1984, LB 897
